ast year's winner Jessica Warner-Judd.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"score\": 0.9242219461682043, \"rank\": 0.08199041818987314, \"text\": \"Jessica\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Simpson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stellar field\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"home rivals\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's winner\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Warner-Judd is the third-fastest Brit of all-time having set her PB of 30:25.93 in 2022 but has not run the Olympic qualifying time within the window for Paris selection having failed to finish at The Ten.\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.4190670794606642e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Warner-Judd\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"the third-fastest Brit\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"all-time\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"her PB\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic qualifying time\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"the window\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"The Ten\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The night of the 10,000m PBs is such a great event every year its bigger and better than it was before,\\\" Judd said.\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The night\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000m PBs\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"such a great event\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"Judd\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not wait to compete on Saturday and be part of such a great day of athletics.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"such a great day\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My last 10k did not quite go to plan, so my aim this weekend is to finish and I can not think of a better place to try and put the demons of my last race behind me!\\\"\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My last 10k\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"plan\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"my aim\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"this weekend\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"a better place\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"the demons\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"my last race\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1917}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Night of the 10,000m PBs launched in 2013 with the aim of providing more opportunities for top-level domestic racing but has since blossomed into one of the circuit's most popular events, attracting athletes from around the world and often doubling as the trials for the summer's major championships.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Night\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000m PBs\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"the aim\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"more opportunities\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"top-level domestic racing\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"the circuit's most popular events\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2117},